{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fc60a7462d","title":"建议","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（三）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编印，1957年10月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8be05bf4dc","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":5,"articleId":"fc60a7462d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0fa7d3988d","name":"山西"},{"id":"2e448713db","name":"张庚"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2c6a01b0f1","type":"title","text":"建议","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc60a7462d"},{"id":"c6a7332c71","type":"authors","text":"山西张庄","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc60a7462d"},{"id":"4aa0a91d5c","type":"subtitle","text":"(张庄：榆次一中教师)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc60a7462d"},{"id":"1def079282","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）把党支部的收音机放到教工俱乐部让全体教工收听当前国内外动态。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc60a7462d"},{"id":"43177b4cf3","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）建议我校党政工团领导干部集体参加大灶一个月，与学生同甘共苦，以体验生活，并希全体同学们热烈地欢迎我们的领导同志。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc60a7462d"},{"id":"816663f534","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）团外学生中模范很多，建议教导处把没进行选举的原因向全校学生加以解释，这样他们就不会再认为学生中有一大群私生子了。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc60a7462d"},{"id":"a0dad20f37","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）建议同学对害党害人民的假积极分子，不管是谁，只要看准了就把他的丑恶鬼脸揭露出来，然后团结教育他，给他治病。但不要忙着结束争鸣。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc60a7462d"},{"id":"b132ea814f","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）建议同学们要用严肃正直的态度，对待问题，不要胡闹，也不要忘了给毛主席喊万岁，因为我们的园丁是伟大的毛泽东。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc60a7462d"},{"id":"97e5d85ac5","type":"paragraph","text":" 榆次一中教师  张庄1957年6月5日","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc60a7462d"}],"page":{"id":"4531a06266","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc60a7462d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}